ful flash performance of a professional studio flash. Even in the darkest of environments, it delivers stunning results. In settings like city neon lights, hallways, tunnels, and other low-light scenes, the Vintage Z1 effortlessly creates the perfect ambiance with a single flash, delivering high-quality portraiture and instantly creating cinematic shots. The darker it gets, the better the shots,” \u003ca href=\"https://viltrox.com/products/vintage-z1-camera-flash\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"follow external noopener\"\u003eViltrox explains.\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_791819\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-791819\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/Viltrox-Z1-Flash-PetaPixel-BG-Sample-Night-Images-800x420.jpg\" alt=\"A young woman wearing headphones poses in various locations: by the waterfront with city lights and ferris wheels in the background, and indoors with a boombox, bookshelves, and a lit lamp behind her.\" width=\"800\" height=\"420\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/Viltrox-Z1-Flash-PetaPixel-BG-Sample-Night-Images-800x420.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/Viltrox-Z1-Flash-PetaPixel-BG-Sample-Night-Images-320x168.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/Viltrox-Z1-Flash-PetaPixel-BG-Sample-Night-Images-1536x806.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/Viltrox-Z1-Flash-PetaPixel-BG-Sample-Night-Images-150x79.jpg 150w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/Viltrox-Z1-Flash-PetaPixel-BG-Sample-Night-Images-300x157.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/Viltrox-Z1-Flash-PetaPixel-BG-Sample-Night-Images-400x209.jpg 400w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/Viltrox-Z1-Flash-PetaPixel-BG-Sample-Night-Images-550x288.jpg 550w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/04/Viltrox-Z1-Flash-PetaPixel-BG-Sample-Night-Images.jpg 1600w\" siz